 of a first order\nstructural phase transition from the trigonal (P-3m1) phase at higher\npressures. We estimate the start of this structural phase transition to be 8\nGPa and the symmetric of the new high-pressure phase to be monoclinic (C2/m).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Sep 2017 05:47:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-14"}
